        5/8/2017
    

Without question the worst customer service of any utility or customer focused organization that I have ever dealt with.  You cannot talk to anyone who makes a decision or schedules people.  Having problems with your meter, they tell you to plan to wait all day.Want a meter moved, they contract that out to someone and do not plan to get it ever scheduled.Want to talk to a scheduler for either.  They are not available and the customer service line will tell you they are not allowed to talk to themWhen they came to move the meter, they told me I needed a new line from the meter to the street.  This is an expense they need to incur, I have never heard back from them.Without question, the CEO of Washington Gas should be the next CEO of United Airlines, because they would be my all stars for pathetic approaches to customers.




