                                                                     Get the peace of mind you deserve with our RescueLock 12 fixed rate plan!• Enroll on RescueLock 12 and 5% of your monthly energy charges will be donated to PetSmart Charities!*• Lock in your rate for 12 full months• Get stability for the duration of your term• Protect yourself from the uncertainty that you've come to expect with energy bills.Rate above is available to customers enrolling with XOOM Energy for the first time.Rate above applies to all therms used.XOOM Energy Maryland License No.  IR-2446


