        7/1/2017
    

Washington Gas turned off the gas to my house because they were fixing a leak in their system at the street. They left a note on the door at 4 am on Thursday 6/29 saying they had turned off the gas. I don't use the door where they left the note, so I saw it Sat morning 7/1 and called to have the gas turned back on, but was told that Washington Gas doesn't work on weekends so it would be Monday at the earliest that they could turn the gas back on. Unbelievable. They can't turn the gas on because Washington Gas technicians don't work weekends. I have been paying my bill on time at this address for 31 years. Now I'm stuck with no hot water or gas to cook with for at least the weekend. Terrible customer service. Especially for a utility that the public depends on.




