        7/12/2017
    

Rating systems need to have negative stars for "messed up" circumstances.When calling for service you have to wait the entire day because they do not give time windows.  If they don't show up then oh, well try again another day.  They are very good at turning your gas off.  Not so much with getting it turned back on.  Some techs call but most don't.  One showed up about two to three days after I called (at a time when no one would be home).  I am literally at the complaining to third parties stage.  Seriously consider going all electric if you have the funds.  I even received a gas delivery charge when my house currently has no gas for about a month.




